embeddableConfig.description: Monitor thread states to understand connection patterns. High `created` counts with low `cached` may indicate `thread_cache_size` needs tuning. Running threads approaching connected threads indicates high concurrency.
embeddableConfig.title: Threads - by State

embeddableConfig.description: Replication lag > 30s indicates the replica is falling behind. Check network bandwidth, disk I/O on replica, or long-running transactions on primary. Lag > 60s may indicate failover readiness issues.
embeddableConfig.title: Replication Lag

embeddableConfig.description: Any non-zero error count should be investigated. `max_connections` errors indicate pool exhaustion. `aborted_clients` may indicate application issues or network problems.
embeddableConfig.title: Connection Errors - by Type
